com.amfontai.cmput301asn1

Class NotesList

  • java.lang.Object
    • ListActivity
      • com.amfontai.cmput301asn1.NotesList

  • public class NotesList
extends ListActivity
    The Class NotesList represents an ListActivity that lists all the Notes that are saved in the DB. The Notes are listed in order of most recent date (but the order is set by the NotesDb class). The ListAdapter is a SimpleCursorAdapter returned to the activity by the DB. The list view is defined in activity_notes_list.xml
